ridge University Press|location=Port Melbourne, Victoria|isbn=0-521-76345-2|ref=harv}} * {{cite book |last1=Wall|first1=Don|last2=Seale|first2=Clem|title=Singapore and Beyond: The Story of the Men of the 2/20 Battalion Told by the Survivors |year=1985 |publisher=Griffin Press |location=Netley, South Australia |isbn= 9780958984300 |ref=harv }} *{{cite book|last=Wigmore|first=Lionel|title=The Japanese Thrust |url=https://www.awm.gov.au/collection/RCDIG1070203/|edition=First |series=Australia in the War of 1939–1945. Series 1 – Army|volume=Volume 4|year=1957|publisher=Australian War Memorial|location=Canberra, Australian Capital Territory|oclc=3134219|ref=harv}}
